text: Krzysztof Birula-Białynicki (15 August 1944 – 30 January 2014)Bialynicki- Birula passes away was a Polish ice hockey player. He competed at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==Notes== Category:1944 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Polish ice hockey players Category:Olympians for Poland
